data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming duplex situated in sought-after Spring Lake, MI. This property offers a great location near parks, and the magnificent beaches of Lake Michigan, complemented by the highly-rated Grand Haven schools. Each unit features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a kitchen with a separate dining area, and a spacious living room. Additionally, enjoy the practicality of laundry hookups in each unit and the added convenience of a 2-car garage. Step outside onto the deck and patio, where you can unwind while overlooking the serene 1/2-acre park-like yard. This property presents an incredible opportunity for both investors and homeowners alike. Seller requests all offers be held until Tuesday April 23rd at 12:00 PM. Property being sold AS IS.
